Our Pharmacy Services put you first

Just like most neighborhood pharmacies, you can walk right in, fill your prescriptions and buy whatever you need. What’s different at Vital Care Pharmacy? Our personalized approach! We care!
As a family-owned pharmacy who has been part of the Pikesville community for 20+ years, we careabout relationships as much as we care about top-notch service.

Why choose us?

At Vital Care Pharmacy and Health Rite Medical Supply, we do everything
possible to make getting your prescriptions a breeze, including:

  • Free same day delivery!

  • Prescriptions filled in Chinese, Korean, Spanish, Russian, and Vietnamese

  • Drug information sheet in your language

  • Contacting doctors on your behalf

  • Free individual consultation with the Pharmacist

  • High-copay discussion before order

  • Best prices on the market

  • We help to choose the right Medicare Part D plan

  • Drug recall management

  • Prior Authorization Assistance

  • Assistance with non-covered medications

  • Multiple packaging options (vials, bubble cards)

From hygiene essentials like shampoo and toothpaste to medical supplies like compression stockings, we have everything you need to support good health.

We carry a full line of vitamins, supplements and an herbal line, too!

We offerFREE delivery

on all orders to Baltimore County, Carroll County, Montgomery County, Harford County, Howard County and beyond!
